<td>S</td>
<td>S</td>
<td>S</td>
<td>S
</td></tr></tbody></table>
<p>The player has a height of 2 blocks, 
and needs one more free space above to climb stairs.
</p>
<table class="wikitable">

<tbody><tr>
<th>Resources</th>
<th>Type</th>
<th>Amount needed
</th></tr>
<tr>
<td>Tools</td>
<td>-none-</td>
<td>-none-
</td></tr>
