<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Cavehome_2">Cavehome 2</span></h3>
<p>This is the expanded version of the 'small/short' <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://wiki.minetest.net/Building_a_home#Cave-home_.2F_Bunker">Cave-Home/Bunker</a> above.<br />
Enlarged to a room of size 3x4, with
torches, door, furnace, some chests, bed,<br />
and a ladder that leads down to the start of the mining-area.
</p><p>The stones that were dug out have been used to make the furnace,<br />
the stairs and pavement outside the entrance, and for new stonetools.
</p>
<table>

<tbody><tr>
<td><div class="thumb tright"><div class="thumbinner" style="width:302px;"><a href="/File:CaveHome2-0.png" class="image"><img alt="" src="/images/thumb/7/7f/CaveHome2-0.png/300px-CaveHome2-0.png" decoding="async" width="300" height="225" class="thumbimage" srcset="/images/thumb/7/7f/CaveHome2-0.png/450px-CaveHome2-0.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7f/CaveHome2-0.png/600px-CaveHome2-0.png 2x" /></a>  <div class="thumbcaption"><div class="magnify"><a href="/File:CaveHome2-0.png" class="internal" title="Enlarge"></a></div>Entrance with door and stairs.</div></div></div></td>
<td><div class="thumb tright"><div class="thumbinner" style="width:302px;"><a href="/File:CaveHome2-1.png" class="image"><img alt="" src="/images/thumb/8/89/CaveHome2-1.png/300px-CaveHome2-1.png" decoding="async" width="300" height="225" class="thumbimage" srcset="/images/thumb/8/89/CaveHome2-1.png/450px-CaveHome2-1.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/89/CaveHome2-1.png/600px-CaveHome2-1.png 2x" /></a>  <div class="thumbcaption"><div class="magnify"><a href="/File:CaveHome2-1.png" class="internal" title="Enlarge"></a></div>Cavehome with basic furniture</div></div></div></td>
