<p>In total, this whole building (except for the bed) needs about 3 trees and 1 block of coal-ore.
</p>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Nicer_Houses">Nicer Houses</span></h3>
<p>For working with stone, we need tools.<br />
Wooden tools are slow, and wear out fast, 
so you should make stone tools with the first few stones you get.
</p><p>Here some examples of houses:
</p>
