<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Small_House_7x7">Small House 7x7</span></h4>
<p>This is my 'standard' design for a simple small house.<br />
The inner living space is 5x5,
and with a path and a fence around the house,<br />
it will fit within the 11x11 area covered by one protection-block.
</p>
<table class="wikitable">

<tbody><tr>
<td>g</td>
