<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Starter_House_7x7">Starter House 7x7</span></h4>
<p>As above, but a simplified design to be built by a <a href="/Mods/digtron" title="Mods/digtron">DigTron</a>,<br />
eg. as welcome-present for starting players, or to quickly set up a village.
</p><p>The inner living space is 5x5,
and it can be built complete with interior,<br />
eg. bed, chest, furnace, table&amp;chair, light (eg. a slice of glowglass).
</p>
