<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Realistic_House_8x10">Realistic House 8x10</span></h4>
<p>'Realistic' in the sense that the inside is divided into several rooms,
eg. kitchen, living room, bathroom, bedroom. 
</p><p>Rooms need at least 2x2 (eg. bed/chest/furnace + free space to stand on), 
plus surrounding walls/door/window.
</p><p>Mods such as xdecor or homedecor will make it look much nicer than plain MTG.
</p>
