<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Small_Tower_5x5">Small Tower 5x5</span></h4>
<p>We alter between solid rows of stone,
and rows with a hole in the side. <br />
Running along the inside of the walls, we put stairs (simple dirt for now),<br />
and the center gets filled with leaves during the construction.
</p>
