<p>W=wall x=alternating wall/window  d=dirt/stairs  #=leaves or ladder as filler
</p><p>In one of the walls in the bottom row
the center stone gets removed, to make a door.
</p><p>The holes in the sides can later be filled with glass, to make proper windows.
</p><p>...
</p>
<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Bigger_Tower_9x9">Bigger Tower 9x9</span></h4>
<p>Another square floorplan, so it can also serve as a regular house.
</p>
